title: Egg Farm
description: Egg Farm is an arcade game where you play as a fox who needs to catch all the delicious chicken eggs inside your mouth! It's time to become an egg-cellent egg-catching maestro, but you need to be careful and not eat rotten eggs. Focus on the types of eggs because they can be either helpful or harmful to you.
